        <body>
            <pb facs="MSVIII77r"/>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" rhyme="aababccbbddeffeegghgijklmnonnppqqrrssttuvnvww" met="-+|-+|-+|-+">
                <head type="title"><handShift new="#HANDJR1826-27" script="cursive" medium="ink"/><placeName corresp="#GENOA">Genoa</placeName></head>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Now rouse thee ho. For <placeName corresp="#GENOA">Genoa</placeName> straight</l>
                    <l>We did not for the dawning wait</l>
                    <l>The stars shone pale on <placeName corresp="#NOVI">Novi</placeName>s Gate<!-- I think this is Novi's Gate. CDM -->,</l>
                    <l>And on the airy <geogName corresp="#APENNINE">Apennine</geogName> <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1380</add></l>
                    <l>Whose towery steeps, with morn elate,</l>
                    <l>Lay southward in a lengthened line</l>
                    <l>And we knew, and we knew, and we knew</l>
                    <l>That from <geogName corresp="#ELBA">Elba</geogName> to the <geogName corresp="#Alps">Alps</geogName>, oer the seas broad blue</l>
                    <l>Where the wild waves wander, and white ripples shine <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1385</add></l>
                    <l>Looked the cloudy crest of the tall <geogName corresp="#APENNINE">Apennine</geogName></l>
                    <l>From the Torrents barren bed,</l>
                    <l>Bound by blocks of granite red,</l>
                    <l>Came the gay Cicadas song</l>
                    <l>Wheresoeer the dew was dank, <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1390</add></l>
                    <l>On the tree, the shrub the bank,</l>
                    <l>All our scorching road along</l>
                    <l>Came the gay Cicadas song,</l>
                    <l>While beside our path was seen</l>
                    <l>Of various trees a vista green;<!-- An ink mark here CDM  --> <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1395</add></l>
                    <l>Into a streamlet looking down </l>
                    <l>Whose living <unclear>crystal shot</unclear> between, <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">8.50</add></l> <!-- The unclear text is my best guess and I recommend it be checked for accuracy CDM -->
                    <l><del rend="strikethrough">A <add place="above">XXX</add> <unclear>wide</unclear> space of Time</del></l>
                    <l><del rend="strikethrough">And think <unclear>love</unclear> with the world would be</del></l>
                    <l><del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>Acrost</unclear> from pole to pole</del></l>
                    <l><del rend="strikethrough">When &#x2038;<add place="above"><space quantity="6" unit= "chars"/>all</add> that there you love after</del> <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">X 80</add><!-- No idea why X 80 is here CDM --></l>
                    <l><add>Oh</add>  <!-- The addition of "Oh" is placed within the margin CDM--> <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>And</unclear></del> is there one remembered with</l>
                    <l>When first he saw the living deep,</l>
                    <pb facs="MSVIII79v"/>
                    <l>With panting bosom, crimson shot,</l>
                    <l>Call its soothed billows from their sleep,</l>
                    <l>That shout<space quantity="3" unit="chars"/>The mo<del rend="overwrite">a</del>rn, from steep to steep. <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1400</add></l>
                    <l>When far away to seaward show.</l>
                    <l>Her first beamed solitary glow. <!-- Curving zigzagging scribble on manuscript that extends down to dwelt CDM --></l>
                    <l>Whoe'r thou art, who hast not felt</l>
                    <l>Thou lovedst to be where seabirds dwelt. </l>
                    <l>To wander on the weary beach <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1405</add></l>
                    <l>Just on the line the wild waves reach,</l>
                    <l>Or watch the petals flit before</l>
                    <l>The marching tempests warning roar.</l>
                    <l>And ocean eagles dark and proud,</l>
                    <l>And white winged ospreys skim the cloud <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1410</add></l>
                    <l>And if thou neer hast felt as if</l>
                    <l>The ocean had a mind</l>
                    <l><del rend="overwrite">And</del>Nor held communion with the deep</l>
                    <l>And converse with the wind</l>
                    <l>When broad black waves before it roll &#x2014; <add rend="linenumber-right-JR">1415</add></l>
                    <l>I would not think thou thadst a soul.</l>
                    <!-- The paper of the manuscript is lined CDM -->
                </lg>
